dct_title_s: Map of the Comstock Lodes extending down Gold Cañon : Storey Co., Nevada
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Oriented with north toward right. From: Statement and reports concerning the Uncle Sam Senior and Gold Cañon silver lodes in Nevada / [Samuel A. Chapin]. 1865.
